                  <h1 class="heavy text-white"><span class="carousel-title-bgclear">smalltalkto.me</span></h1><br>
                  <h3 class="text-white">It's a big world out there, but we're here at help. If you're feeling nervous about an upcoming social event, <b>smalltalkto.me</b> is the resource for you. We have have plenty of conversation tips and some great stories for you to share</h3>
                </div>
              </div>


            </div><!-- /content container -->
          </div><!-- /container -->
        </div><!-- /bg div -->
      </div><!-- /item -->
      <!-- End Item 1 -->

      <!-- Begin Item 2 -->

        <!-- Begin Item 1 -->
        <div class="item">
          <!-- Item BG -->
          <div class="background-main" style="background-image:url('<%= asset_path("backgrounds/bg2.jpg") %>');" data-0="background-position:0px 0px;" data-500="background-position:0px -250px;">
            <div class="container">
              <div class="row carousel-content center-vertically">
                <!-- Content -->
                <div class="fadeInTop-animated" data-animation="fadeInTop">
                  <div class="carousel-description col-sm-12">
                    <h1 class="heavy text-white"><span class="carousel-title-bgclear">smalltalkto.me</span></h1><br>
                    <h3 class="text-white">Would a back-up plan make your life a little better? We are here to help there too. Just schedule a call below and smalltalk will call with an emergency. The perfect out.</h3>
